"es-ES\">Aram.</span>, </span><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" lang=\"es-ES\">gat. </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">Recipiente grande para pisar uvas</span>, </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">generalmente excavado en la roca</span>, </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">y que tenía conductos para que el jugo fluyera hacia recipientes a desnivel bajo donde éste fermentara. En este caso</span>, </span><span style=\"\" lang=\"es-ES\">Gedeón utilizó el lagar para trillar las espigas a escondidas para que no lo vieran los medianitas.</span></p><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\"></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1050","title":"Jueces 6:17","author":"Instituto Cultural Álef y Tau, A.C.","reference":{"book":"JDG","chapterStart":6,"verseStart":17,"chapterEnd":6,"verseEnd":17},"content":"<span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>a</sup></span> </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b2.4.1-9'>Éxo 4:1-9</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b7.6.37'>Jue 6:37</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b7.6.39'>Jue 6:39</a></span></p></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1051","title":"Jueces 6:22","author":"Instituto Cultural Álef y Tau, A.C.","reference":{"book":"JDG","chapterStart":6,"verseStart":22,"chapterEnd":6,"verseEnd":22},"content":"<span style=\"color:#0000FF;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\"><sup>a</sup></span> </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b1.32.30'>Gén 32:30</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b2.33.20'>Éxo 33:20</a></span>; </span><span style=\"color:#008000;text-decoration:underline;\"><a class=\"bible\" href='#b7.13.21-22'>Jue 13:21-22</a></span></p></span></p>"},{"id":"peshitta-notas-1052","title":"Jueces 6:24